live up to it, and never let you go ♪

00:03:37.680 --> 00:03:38.810
besides killing...

00:03:41.260 --> 00:03:41.820
it

00:03:43.030 --> 00:03:43.820
might also have

00:03:43.820 --> 00:03:44.040
another purpose.

00:03:44.040 --> 00:03:46.430
♪ Listen to the rain ♪

00:03:46.720 --> 00:03:46.750
