00:04:36.820 --> 00:04:38.030
called

00:04:38.409 --> 00:04:38.940
♪ On the way back, a half-lit oil lamp ♪

00:04:38.940 --> 00:04:40.000
the Tianren Realm.

00:04:41.159 --> 00:04:41.659
♪ Wet ink stains surge and overflow ♪

00:04:41.659 --> 00:04:42.860
The Tianren Realm...

00:04:44.590 --> 00:04:46.100
♪ Hope what's hopeful,
and let go of anger in a day ♪

00:04:46.100 --> 00:04:46.960
Alright, Lici.

00:04:47.790 --> 00:04:49.190
If we don't practice now,

00:04:49.420 --> 00:04:50.620
