00:04:51.350 --> 00:04:51.510
♪ Yearn for what's yearnable,
live up to it, and never let you go ♪

00:04:51.510 --> 00:04:52.350
You can

00:04:52.980 --> 00:04:53.710
tell me

00:04:53.710 --> 00:04:55.370
those things in detail later.

00:05:54.950 --> 00:05:55.550
Fang Zhou,

00:05:56.510 --> 00:05:57.770
I've never understood

00:05:58.810 --> 00:06:00.070
why we can't tell them.

00:06:01.790 --> 00:06:02.660
Man on earth,

00:06:03.450 --> 00:06:04.280
good at birth.

00:06:05.920 --> 00:06:07.390
We're doing good deeds.

00:06:08.780 --> 00:06:10.240
But why can't we tell them?

00:06:13.670 --> 00:06:14.480
Joy and anger,

00:06:15.480 --> 00:06:16.410
sorrow and fear,

00:06:17.560 --> 00:06:18.890
love, hate, and desire—

00:06:19.120 --> 00:06:20.250
the seven emotions.

00:06:21.280 --> 00:06:21.800
Lici.

00:06:22.840 --> 00:06:25.240
They're just ordinary people in Shenzhou,

00:06:25.520 --> 00:06:26.920
with all seven emotions.

00:06:27.450 --> 00:06:28.090
Perhaps

00:06:28.750 --> 00:06:30.150
this will make them angry

00:06:30.430 --> 00:06:32.230
and lead to misunderstandings.

00:06:32.920 --> 00:06:33.990
When you travel

00:06:34.400 --> 00:06:36.400
throughout Shenzhou in the future,

00:06:36.440 --> 00:06:37.970
you'll come to understand.

00:07:01.710 --> 00:07:02.470
Mr. Tang.

00:07:15.010 --> 00:07:15.620
Mr. Tang.

00:07:16.580 --> 00:07:17.780
Who is this statue of?

00:07:18.660 --> 00:07:20.190
You've always been clever.

00:07:20.550 --> 00:07:21.480
Can't you guess?

00:07:23.420 --> 00:07:25.300
