00:07:28.210 --> 00:07:29.740
Now, thanks to a certain someone,

00:07:29.740 --> 00:07:31.250
whenever this name is mentioned,

00:07:31.250 --> 00:07:32.780
I think of a different face.

00:07:33.740 --> 00:07:34.740
You rarely

00:07:34.870 --> 00:07:36.600
let small matters trouble you.

00:07:39.460 --> 00:07:41.730
The Sword Alliance is going to
eliminate Fengliu Shop.

00:07:41.730 --> 00:07:44.350
There are both internal
and external troubles.

00:07:44.350 --> 00:07:45.350
But I believe

00:07:45.630 --> 00:07:47.800
you'll always find a way
to overcome difficulties.

00:07:47.800 --> 00:07:49.460
Just like the wooden carving.

00:07:50.310 --> 00:07:52.110
Even if it's difficult to carve,

00:07:52.140 --> 00:07:54.010
it can still resemble
the original somewhat.

00:07:54.010 --> 00:07:55.820
Even if it can't become a masterpiece,

00:07:55.820 --> 00:07:57.420
it can still serve a purpose.

00:08:08.800 --> 00:08:10.690
[Zhoudi Tower]

00:08:20.000 --> 00:08:21.040
Zhoudi Tower?

00:08:22.940 --> 00:08:24.530
Let me see

00:08:24.870 --> 00:08:25.820
