00:08:25.820 --> 00:08:27.030
are hidden within.

00:08:30.820 --> 00:08:32.100
Fang Zhou's heart crystal

00:08:32.100 --> 00:08:33.299
is now inside my body,

00:08:33.679 --> 00:08:34.610
and his body

00:08:34.760 --> 00:08:36.549
has been hidden by me in Zhoudi Tower,

00:08:36.549 --> 00:08:37.380
preserved in the Immortal Crystal Coffin

00:08:37.380 --> 00:08:38.669
from Biluo Palace.

00:08:39.030 --> 00:08:40.260
As long as I use the Rebirth Scroll

00:08:40.260 --> 00:08:41.190
to restore it,

00:08:42.059 --> 00:08:42.789
Fang Zhou

00:08:43.580 --> 00:08:44.580
can be revived.

00:08:45.980 --> 00:08:46.610
Yan.

00:08:47.350 --> 00:08:48.470
Give me back the other half

00:08:48.470 --> 00:08:49.730
of the Rebirth Scroll.

00:08:49.740 --> 00:08:51.800
Let's bring Fang Zhou back together.

00:08:52.470 --> 00:08:53.500
Tang Lici is

00:08:54.050 --> 00:08:55.710
Yique Yinyang.

00:08:55.730 --> 00:08:57.060
He's extremely cunning

00:08:57.170 --> 00:08:59.070
and excels at distorting the truth.

00:08:59.070 --> 00:09:00.530
Don't believe his words.

00:09:01.060 --> 00:09:02.790
You have to trust your own eyes.

00:09:21.110 --> 00:09:22.170
Shen, you're back.

00:09:23.730 --> 00:09:25.530
Is there news from my godfather?

00:09:30.100 --> 00:09:31.030
Thank you, Shen.

00:09:44.390 --> 00:09:45.180
Mr. Tang.

00:09:48.310 --> 00:09:49.040
Master Shao.

00:09:50.250 --> 00:09:52.780
You're reading
the Three Character Classic.

00:09:54.940 --> 00:09:55.430
What?

00:09:57.060 --> 00:09:58.060
Master Shao, you think

00:09:58.060 --> 00:09:59.390
I'm too old to be reading

00:09:59.540 --> 00:10:00.220
this now?

00:10:00.390 --> 00:10:01.420
No, no.

00:10:01.530 --> 00:10:03.800
He who reflects on the past
and gains insight from it is fit to teach.

00:10:03.800 --> 00:10:04.860
Didn't you take Stone

00:10:04.860 --> 00:10:05.860
as your disciple?

00:10:06.310 --> 00:10:07.550
Teaching him the Three Character Classic

00:10:07.550 --> 00:10:08.230
is perfect.

00:10:09.540 --> 00:10:11.440
I'm just teaching him a few characters.

00:10:11.440 --> 00:10:12.840
He's hardly my disciple.

00:10:14.220 --> 00:10:15.220
If you say so,

00:10:15.300 --> 00:10:16.570
then he's not.

00:10:22.340 --> 00:10:23.550
Master Shao, you look

00:10:23.550 --> 00:10:25.060
so worried and gloomy again.

00:10:25.060 --> 00:10:27.150
Is something important troubling you?

00:10:27.150 --> 00:10:29.150
I received a message from Master Ji.

00:10:30.680 --> 00:10:33.460
He said it's been rather unsettled
out there recently.

00:10:33.460 --> 00:10:34.630
Several of our disciples

00:10:34.630 --> 00:10:36.030
who were away on missions

00:10:36.230 --> 00:10:38.430
were brutally killed by the Fengliu Shop.

00:10:38.430 --> 00:10:40.090
More than 10 have been killed.

00:10:40.580 --> 00:10:41.430
I'll go back and practice as well.

00:10:41.430 --> 00:10:42.060
Alright.

00:10:54.790 --> 00:10:55.910
This killing method

00:10:55.910 --> 00:10:57.280
doesn't seem like Fengliu Shop's work,

00:10:57.280 --> 00:10:59.420
but more like an assassin's technique.

00:10:59.420 --> 00:11:01.020
Sixth Sword Master, well...

00:11:02.990 --> 00:11:04.790
Unable to confront us directly,

00:11:05.700 --> 00:11:07.760
they've resorted to assassination.

00:11:07.800 --> 00:11:08.930
This is outrageous.

00:11:12.470 --> 00:11:13.650
Send a message to Master Shao immediately.

00:11:13.650 --> 00:11:14.180
Yes!

00:11:19.120 --> 00:11:19.780
It's a trap.

00:11:20.700 --> 00:11:21.320
Exactly.

00:11:21.890 --> 00:11:23.970
They deliberately chose
this moment to strike—

00:11:23.970 --> 00:11:25.180
it's a trap meant

00:11:25.180 --> 00:11:26.100
to provoke us.

00:11:26.850 --> 00:11:28.630
I'm afraid their hidden agenda

00:11:29.390 --> 00:11:31.050
is more complex than it seems.

00:11:32.860 --> 00:11:33.520
Also,

00:11:34.390 --> 00:11:35.860
there are some rumors

00:11:35.860 --> 00:11:38.120
circulating within the Sword Alliance.

00:11:38.820 --> 00:11:39.580
However,

00:11:40.060 --> 00:11:41.270
I'm already tracking down

00:11:41.270 --> 00:11:42.800
the source of those rumors.

00:11:47.680 --> 00:11:49.210
Master Shao, do you know...

00:11:50.340 --> 00:11:51.510
a fortune-teller has joined

00:11:51.510 --> 00:11:52.770
the alliance recently, and he's

00:11:52.770 --> 00:11:55.470
-doing odd jobs in the Service Hall?
-After Mr. Tang came here,

00:11:55.470 --> 00:11:58.200
though your basic needs
are well provided for...

00:11:59.030 --> 00:12:00.200
have your lives...

00:12:02.220 --> 00:12:03.460
truly gotten better?

00:12:04.100 --> 00:12:05.580
Fengliu Shop keeps attacking

00:12:05.580 --> 00:12:06.590
you alliance disciples.

00:12:06.590 --> 00:12:08.920
Are you just going to swallow this insult?

00:12:09.910 --> 00:12:10.880
Perhaps Mr. Tang is

00:12:10.880 --> 00:12:12.310
making careful plans.

00:12:13.540 --> 00:12:14.220
Plans?

00:12:15.330 --> 00:12:16.390
What kind of plans?

00:12:16.910 --> 00:12:17.940
That we don't know.

00:12:17.940 --> 00:12:19.100
But I believe Mr. Tang

00:12:19.100 --> 00:12:21.080
certainly won't stand by and do nothing.

00:12:21.080 --> 00:12:21.780
Indeed.

00:12:22.710 --> 00:12:24.310
Since he keeps saying

00:12:24.340 --> 00:12:25.550
he wants to eliminate Fengliu Shop,

00:12:25.550 --> 00:12:26.980
why does he only teach you

00:12:26.980 --> 00:12:28.580
lightness skills for escape

00:12:28.600 --> 00:12:31.330
and sword formations
that merely delay enemies?

00:12:32.260 --> 00:12:34.890
No matter how well-coordinated
your sword formations are,

00:12:34.890 --> 00:12:35.860
can they allow you to take the initiative

00:12:35.860 --> 00:12:37.460
and eliminate Fengliu Shop?

00:12:37.840 --> 00:12:39.480
Or can they protect you

00:12:40.030 --> 00:12:42.230
from enemy ambushes when you're alone?

00:12:43.070 --> 00:12:44.180
That makes some sense.

00:12:44.180 --> 00:12:44.640
Indeed.

00:12:46.280 --> 00:12:47.730
I can't dispute that.

00:12:49.440 --> 00:12:50.570
I've heard about it.

00:12:51.270 --> 00:12:51.910
What?

00:12:52.440 --> 00:12:54.210
Is there something wrong with him?

00:12:54.210 --> 00:12:55.050
A serious one.

00:12:56.220 --> 00:12:56.910
Then...

00:12:57.160 --> 00:12:58.040
I'll have someone

00:12:58.040 --> 00:12:59.170
bring him to see you?

00:12:59.910 --> 00:13:00.370
No rush.

00:13:01.100 --> 00:13:02.300
When Chi Yun returns,

00:13:02.510 --> 00:13:03.710
I'll find him myself.

00:13:05.350 --> 00:13:06.270
I hear it.

00:13:07.130 --> 00:13:08.810
Someone is calling my name.

00:13:09.930 --> 00:13:10.650
Are you

00:13:11.590 --> 00:13:12.740
really

00:13:13.350 --> 00:13:14.080
desperately

00:13:14.450 --> 00:13:15.710
in need of me right now?

00:13:23.630 --> 00:13:24.550
The capable bear more work.

00:13:24.550 --> 00:13:25.630
I guess I'll have to do you a favor

00:13:25.630 --> 00:13:27.230
and run this errand for you, Foxy Tang.

00:13:27.230 --> 00:13:28.890
You seem quite happy about it.

00:13:38.460 --> 00:13:40.220
I just find it strange—

00:13:40.620 --> 00:13:43.220
since Mr. Tang has
unmatched martial arts skills,

00:13:43.220 --> 00:13:44.750
why doesn't he teach those skills

00:13:44.750 --> 00:13:46.060
to each one of us?

00:13:47.430 --> 00:13:49.220
If we all improve even a little,

00:13:49.790 --> 00:13:52.100
when the final battle
with Fengliu Shop comes,

00:13:52.100 --> 00:13:53.180
each of us could

00:13:53.180 --> 00:13:54.580
contribute more, right?

00:13:55.070 --> 00:13:55.980
Mr. Tang probably

00:13:55.980 --> 00:13:57.310
wouldn't need that extra help, would he?

00:13:57.310 --> 00:13:58.390
Am I right?

00:13:58.390 --> 00:13:59.060
-Yes.
-Yeah.

00:13:59.060 --> 00:13:59.460
That's right.

00:13:59.460 --> 00:14:00.180
Indeed.

00:14:02.310 --> 00:14:04.440
Well, Mr. Tang is so confident

00:14:04.710 --> 00:14:05.910
that he's staking everything

00:14:05.910 --> 00:14:06.910
on himself alone.

00:14:07.060 --> 00:14:07.580
What if

00:14:07.580 --> 00:14:08.630
he never actually intended to

00:14:08.630 --> 00:14:10.350
destroy Fengliu Shop in the first place?

00:14:10.350 --> 00:14:12.080
Wouldn't we all be doomed then?

00:14:12.340 --> 00:14:13.670
Use your brains, guys.

00:14:16.430 --> 00:14:17.550
How impressive

00:14:17.550 --> 00:14:19.810
that you possess such insight, Mr. Fang.

00:14:22.540 --> 00:14:23.070
Mr. Tang.

